Not really wanting to start an argument, but you might want to rethink your animosity towards twinks because twinking is only going to get worse.<br>
<br>
At this point in its life EQ is all about replayability. Look at the various changes to low level play VI has implemented.  VI has also given away GAME KEYS. VI did these things in order to help people create twinks and stay playing the game.<br>
<br>
If twinking really causes you that much anguish I suggest try playing on FV. I know it has implemented Trivial Loot Code. I do not know for sure how that impacts twinking, but I would think that it significantly reduces it. <p>Kurrlee<br>
